                    <p class="fs-5">
                        To download the Level Editor <a href="https://github.com/mmmdule/RetroFPS-LevelEditor/releases/download/demo/LevelEditor.Standalone.faster.zip" class="text-danger text-decoration-none">click here</a>.
                        After downloading the file, unzip it and run the executable file titled <b>"LevelEditor.exe"</b>.
                    </p>
                    <p class="fs-5">
                        The Level Editor is a standalone application, meaning that it does not require the game to be installed in order to run.
                        Once you install the Level Editor, you can start creating your own levels right away.
                        Create a level pack and add levels and story segments to it. Once you are done, you can share your level pack with the community.
                    </p>
                    <p class="fs-5">
